{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "vermogenspeil-api-v1",
    "name": "Vermogenspeil API",
    "description": "MijnVermogen / Vermogenspeil REST API (v1).\n\n**Dev-test zonder broker-accounts (aanbevolen):**\n1. Login → `idToken`\n2. Integrations → **Seed Dev Data** (Bitvavo + DEGIRO demo)\n3. Optioneel: **Import DEGIRO CSV** met `backend/fixtures/degiro/sample-transactions.csv`\n4. Portfolio → **Dashboard Summary**\n\n**Auth:** Bearer `{{idToken}}` na Login.\n\n**baseUrl:** http://localhost:8000/api/v1",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:8000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "testEmail",
      "value": "test@example.com",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "testPassword",
      "value": "SecurePass123!",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "verificationToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "passwordResetToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "idToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "accessToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refreshToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "mfaToken",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "portfolioId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "connectionId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "syncJobId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "bitvavoApiKey",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "bitvavoApiSecret",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "System",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/health/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["health", ""]
            },
            "description": "Publiek endpoint. Verwacht `{\"data\":{\"status\":\"ok\"},...}`"
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "description": "Registratie, login (Auth0 via Django proxy), profiel, wachtwoord reset en MFA reset.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Registration succeeded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.error).to.eql(null);",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email_verified).to.eql(false);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{testPassword}}\",\n  \"first_name\": \"Jan\",\n  \"terms_accepted\": true\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/register/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "register", ""]
            },
            "description": "Maakt Auth0-user + Django-profiel aan. Wachtwoord min. 12 tekens. Geen tokens terug — verificatie vereist.\n\nLokaal: check backend terminal voor verificatie-e-mail (console backend)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Verify Email",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Email verified', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email_verified).to.eql(true);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"token\": \"{{verificationToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-email/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "verify-email", ""]
            },
            "description": "Bevestig e-mail met token uit verificatie-e-mail (24u geldig).\n\nZet `verificationToken` in collection/environment variables."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Resend Verification",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/resend-verification/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "resend-verification", ""]
            },
            "description": "Stuurt nieuwe verificatielink (alleen voor ongeverifieerde accounts). Geeft altijd 200 (geen e-mail enumeration)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('idToken', json.data.id_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.access_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refresh_token);",
                  "    pm.test('Login succeeded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.error).to.eql(null);",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.id_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.access_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}",
                  "",
                  "if (pm.response.code === 403 && json.error === 'mfa_required') {",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('mfaToken', json.data.mfa_token);",
                  "    pm.test('MFA required', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.mfa_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "auth": {
              "type": "noauth"
            },
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{testPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/login/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "login", ""]
            },
            "description": "Login via Django → Auth0 password grant. Blokkeert ongeverifieerde users (`email_not_verified`).\n\nSucces: slaat `idToken`, `accessToken`, `refreshToken` op.\n\nMFA: bij `403 mfa_required` wordt `mfaToken` opgeslagen — voltooi login in de frontend (Auth0 OTP)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Refresh Token",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('idToken', json.data.id_token);",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('accessToken', json.data.access_token);",
                  "    if (json.data.refresh_token) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('refreshToken', json.data.refresh_token);",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.test('Token refreshed', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.id_token).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"refresh\": \"{{refreshToken}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/token/refresh/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "token", "refresh", ""]
            },
            "description": "Vernieuwt Auth0 tokens via Django proxy. Body: `{ \"refresh\": \"...\" }`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Me",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Profile loaded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email).to.be.a('string');",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.email_verified).to.eql(true);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/me/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "me", ""]
            },
            "description": "Profiel van ingelogde user. Vereist Auth0 `id_token` als Bearer token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Request",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"{{testEmail}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password", "reset", ""]
            },
            "description": "Stuurt wachtwoord-resetlink (1u geldig). Geeft altijd 200 (geen e-mail enumeration).\n\nToken uit e-mail → `passwordResetToken`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Validate Token",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset/{{passwordResetToken}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password", "reset", "{{passwordResetToken}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Valideert reset token. Retourneert e-mailadres bij geldige token."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Password Reset Confirm",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"password\": \"NewSecurePass123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/password/reset/{{passwordResetToken}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "password", "reset", "{{passwordResetToken}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Stelt nieuw wachtwoord in (Auth0 + Django token invalidatie). Min. 12 tekens."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/mfa/status/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "mfa", "status", ""]
            },
            "description": "Controleert of OTP-2FA actief is (Auth0 Management API)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Enroll Start",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"password\": \"{{testPassword}}\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/mfa/enroll/start/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "mfa", "enroll", "start", ""]
            },
            "description": "Start 2FA-inschrijving vanuit accountinstellingen. Retourneert `mfa_token` bij `enrollment_required`."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "MFA Reset",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/auth/mfa/reset/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["auth", "mfa", "reset", ""]
            },
            "description": "Verwijdert Auth0 MFA voor ingelogde user. Bij volgende login opnieuw enrollen."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Portfolio",
      "description": "Portefeuilles, posities en transacties (user-scoped). Vereist ingelogde user + geverifieerde e-mail voor koppelingen.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Dashboard Summary",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/portfolios/dashboard/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["portfolios", "dashboard", ""]
            },
            "description": "Totaal, categorieën, platformen, rendement (kostprijs). Run na Seed Dev Data."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Portfolios",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Portfolios returned', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data).to.be.an('array');",
                  "    });",
                  "    if (json.data.length > 0) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('portfolioId', String(json.data[0].id));",
                  "    }",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/portfolios/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["portfolios", ""]
            },
            "description": "Lijst portefeuilles van ingelogde user. Zet `portfolioId` op eerste resultaat."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Portfolio Detail",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/portfolios/{{portfolioId}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["portfolios", "{{portfolioId}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Portefeuille met posities. Vereist `portfolioId` (uit List Portfolios)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Portfolio Transactions",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/portfolios/{{portfolioId}}/transactions/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["portfolios", "{{portfolioId}}", "transactions", ""]
            },
            "description": "Laatste 200 transacties van portefeuille."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Integrations",
      "description": "Platformkoppelingen. Dev: Seed + CSV zonder echte brokers.",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Seed Dev Data",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/demo/seed/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "demo", "seed", ""]
            },
            "description": "Bitvavo + DEGIRO demo-sync. Alleen lokaal (DEMO_FEATURES_ENABLED). Geen API-keys."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Import DEGIRO CSV",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {
                  "key": "file",
                  "type": "file",
                  "src": "backend/fixtures/degiro/sample-transactions.csv"
                }
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/connections/degiro/import/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "connections", "degiro", "import", ""]
            },
            "description": "Upload voorbeeld-CSV uit repo. Postman: kies bestand via file-picker (pad relatief t.o.v. collection werkt niet overal)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "List Connections",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/connections/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "connections", ""]
            },
            "description": "Actieve platformkoppelingen van de user."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Connect Bitvavo",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201 || pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('connectionId', String(json.data.id));",
                  "    if (json.data.sync_job && json.data.sync_job.id) {",
                  "        pm.collectionVariables.set('syncJobId', String(json.data.sync_job.id));",
                  "    }",
                  "    pm.test('Bitvavo connected', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.platform).to.eql('bitvavo');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              },
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"api_key\": \"{{bitvavoApiKey}}\",\n  \"api_secret\": \"{{bitvavoApiSecret}}\",\n  \"label\": \"Bitvavo Postman\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/connections/bitvavo/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "connections", "bitvavo", ""]
            },
            "description": "Koppelt Bitvavo (alleen-lezen keys aanbevolen). Valideert credentials, start sync. Vereist `email_verified`.\n\nZet `bitvavoApiKey` en `bitvavoApiSecret` in environment (niet committen).\n\nProductie: whitelist Render outbound IP bij Bitvavo."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Trigger Sync",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 202) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.collectionVariables.set('syncJobId', String(json.data.id));",
                  "    pm.test('Sync started', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.status).to.be.oneOf(['pending', 'running']);",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/connections/{{connectionId}}/sync/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "connections", "{{connectionId}}", "sync", ""]
            },
            "description": "Start handmatige sync. Slaat `syncJobId` op. Poll daarna Get Sync Job."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Get Sync Job",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    pm.test('Sync job loaded', () => {",
                  "        pm.expect(json.data.status).to.be.a('string');",
                  "    });",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/sync-jobs/{{syncJobId}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "sync-jobs", "{{syncJobId}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Status van sync-taak (`pending` | `running` | `success` | `error`)."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "Delete Connection",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Authorization",
                "value": "Bearer {{idToken}}"
              }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/integrations/connections/{{connectionId}}/",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["integrations", "connections", "{{connectionId}}", ""]
            },
            "description": "Deactiveert koppeling en wist versleutelde API-gegevens."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
